SELECT
        COUNT( DISTINCT IF( t1.relatedId = '-', NULL, t1.relatedId ) ) AS businessCount,
        SUM( IF( t1.inventoryType NOT IN ( 11, 12, 15, 16, 17, 18, 20, 21 ) and t1.inventoryQuantity > 0,
        t1.inventoryQuantity, 0 ) ) AS inStockCount,
        SUM( IF( t1.inventoryType NOT IN ( 11, 12, 15, 16, 17, 18, 20, 21 ) and t1.inventoryQuantity  <  0,
        t1.inventoryQuantity, 0 ) ) AS outStockCount
        FROM
        (
        SELECT
        tsf.stock_flow_id AS stockFlowId,
        IFNULL( tp.main_cover, tsp.attr_pic ) AS mainCover,
        tp.third_code AS thirdCode,
        tp.product_name AS productName,
        tsp.single_product_third_code AS singleProductThirdCode,
        tw.warehouse_name AS warehouseName,
        tsf.inventory_type AS inventoryType,
        tsf.inventory_quantity AS inventoryQuantity,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpots.supplier_name
        WHEN 2 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 3 THEN '-'
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 6 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 7 THEN tprots.supplier_name
        WHEN 8 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 9 THEN '-'
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 12 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 13 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 14 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 15 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 16 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 17 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 18 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 19 THEN IFNULL( trotu.user_name, trotu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 20 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 21 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedName,
        ( tsf.physical_inventory_balance + tsf.occupied_inventory_balance ) AS InventoryBalance,
        tsf.create_date AS createDate,
        tsf.physical_inventory_balance AS physicalInventoryBalance,
        tsf.occupied_inventory_balance AS occupiedInventoryBalance,
        tsf.Intransit_inventory_balance AS IntransitInventoryBalance,
        IFNULL( twr.warehouse_receipt_outer_id, '-' ) AS warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpo.purchase_order_outer_id
        WHEN 2 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 3 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 6 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 7 THEN tpro.purchase_return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 8 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 9 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 12 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 13 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 14 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 15 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 16 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 17 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 18 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 19 THEN tro.return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 20 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 21 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedId,
        tsp.single_product_inner_id AS singleProductInnerId,
        tp.product_inner_id
        FROM
        tenant_stock_flow tsf
        INNER JOIN tenant_product tp ON tsf.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
        AND tp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsf.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
        AND tsp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tsf.warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tsf.oper_user = tea.tea_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt twr ON tsf.warehouse_receipt_id = twr.warehouse_receipt_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order tpo ON tsf.related_id = tpo.purchase_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tpots ON tpo.supplier_id = tpots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order tpro ON tsf.related_id = tpro.purchase_return_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tprots ON tpro.supplier_id = tprots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition tr ON tsf.related_id = tr.requisition_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse outtrtw ON tr.out_warehouse_id = outtrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtrtd ON outtrtw.dealer_id = outtrtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse intrtw ON tr.in_warehouse_id = intrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intrtd ON intrtw.dealer_id = intrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order tcso ON tsf.related_id = tcso.check_stock_order_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tsf.related_id = tor.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tortu ON tor.user_id = tortu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distribution td ON tsf.related_id = td.distribution_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_order tdtdo ON td.distr_order_inner_id = tdtdo.distr_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_initiator_id = intdtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_target_id = outtdtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_return_order tro ON tsf.related_id = tro.return_order_inner_id
        AND tro.return_order_src = 0
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order troto ON tro.order_inner_id = troto.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user trotu ON troto.user_id = trotu.user_inner_id
         WHERE tsf.is_del = 0 
        GROUP BY
        tsf.stock_flow_id
        ) t1
          
        ORDER BY
        t1.stockFlowId DESC,
        t1.product_inner_id DESC

        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedId,

SELECT
            singleProduct.single_product_inner_id AS singleProductInnerId,
            
            singleProduct.thirdCode,
            singleProduct.productName,
            singleProduct.brandName,
            singleProduct.productMainPicUrl,
            singleProduct.combname,
            singleProduct.unitName,
            singleProduct.unitWeight,
            singleProduct.singleProductThirdCode,
            singleProduct.costRice,
            singleProduct.weight,
            singleProduct.volume,
            
            singleProduct.distrProductName,
            singleProduct.distrUnitName,
            singleProduct.distrProductPicUrl,
            singleProduct.distrProductPicUrlDetail,
            singleProduct.stdPrice,
            singleProduct.distrCostRice,
            
            singleProduct.storeProductName,
            singleProduct.storeProductPicUrl,
            singleProduct.retailPrice,
            
            singleProduct.dealerProductName,
            singleProduct.dealerUnitName,
            singleProduct.dealerProductPicUrl,
            singleProduct.dealerRetailPrice,
            singleProduct.dealerDelPrice,
            singleProduct.dealerFreightTemplateName,
            
            tpcav.product_custom_attr_value_id AS customAttrValueId,
            tpca.product_custom_attr_id AS customAttrId,
            tpca.product_custom_attr_field_type AS customAttrFieldType,
            tpca.product_custom_attr_name AS customAttrName,
            tpcae.product_custom_attr_enum_id AS customAttrEnumId,
            ( CASE tpca.product_custom_attr_field_type WHEN 0 THEN tpcav.product_custom_attr_field_eunm WHEN 1 THEN
            tpcae.product_custom_attr_name END ) AS customAttrFieldEunm,
            
            tsaj.single_attr_id AS singleAttrId,
            sbca.cate_attr_inner_id AS attrId,
            sbca.attr_name AS attrName,
            sav.attr_value_id AS attrValueId,
            sav.attr_value AS attrValue,
            sav.attr_code AS attrCode,
            
            tpcavsingle.product_custom_attr_value_id AS singleCustomAttrValueId,
            tpcasingle.product_custom_attr_id AS singleCustomAttrId,
            tpcasingle.product_custom_attr_field_type AS singleCustomAttrFieldType,
            tpcasingle.product_custom_attr_name AS singleCustomAttrName,
            tpcaesingle.product_custom_attr_enum_id AS singleCustomAttrEnumId,
            ( CASE tpcasingle.product_custom_attr_field_type WHEN 0 THEN tpcavsingle.product_custom_attr_field_eunm WHEN 1
            THEN tpcaesingle.product_custom_attr_name END ) AS singleCustomAttrFieldEunm
        FROM
            (
                SELECT
                    
                    product.thirdCode,
                    product.productName,
                    product.brandName,
                    product.productMainPicUrl,
                    product.combname,
                    product.unitName,
                    product.unitWeight,
                    ( CASE tsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tsp.single_product_third_code WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT
                    tspmu.single_product_third_code SEPARATOR ',' ) END ) AS singleProductThirdCode,
                    ( CASE tsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tsp.cost_rice WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tspmu.cost_rice SEPARATOR
                    ',' ) END ) AS costRice,
                    ( CASE tsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tsp.weight WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tspmu.weight SEPARATOR ',' )
                    END ) AS weight,
                    ( CASE tsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tsp.volume WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tspmu.volume SEPARATOR ',' )
                    END ) AS volume,
                    
                    product.distrProductName,
                    product.distrUnitName,
                    product.distrProductPicUrl,
                    product.distrProductPicUrlDetail,
                    ( CASE tdsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tdsp.std_price WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tdspmu.std_price
                    SEPARATOR ',' ) END ) AS stdPrice,
                    ( CASE tdsp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tdsp.cost_rice WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tdspmu.cost_rice
                    SEPARATOR ',' ) END ) AS distrCostRice,
                    
                    product.storeProductName,
                    product.storeProductPicUrl,
                    tssp.retail_price AS retailPrice,
                    
                    product.dealerProductName,
                    product.dealerUnitName,
                    product.dealerProductPicUrl,
                    tosp.retail_price AS dealerRetailPrice,
                    tosp.del_price AS dealerDelPrice,
                    product.dealerFreightTemplateName,
                    
                    product.product_inner_id,
                    tsp.single_product_inner_id
                FROM
                    (
                        SELECT
                            
                            tp.third_code AS thirdCode,
                            tp.product_name AS productName,
                            tb.brand_name AS brandName,
                            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpmp.product_main_pic_url SEPARATOR ',') AS productMainPicUrl,
                            vbcp.combname AS combname,
                            ( CASE tp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tu.name_cn WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpmutu.name_cn SEPARATOR ',' )
                            END ) AS unitName,
                            ( CASE tp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN 1 WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpmu.product_multi_unit_weight
                            SEPARATOR ',' ) END ) AS unitWeight,
                            
                            tdp.distr_product_name AS distrProductName,
                            ( CASE tdp.is_multi_unit WHEN 0 THEN tdptu.name_cn WHEN 1 THEN GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tdpmutu.name_cn SEPARATOR
                            ',' ) END ) AS distrUnitName,
                            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tdpp.distr_product_pic_url SEPARATOR ',' ) AS distrProductPicUrl,
                            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tdppDetail.distr_product_pic_url SEPARATOR ',' ) AS distrProductPicUrlDetail,
                            
                            tsp.store_product_name AS storeProductName,
                            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tspp.store_product_pic_url SEPARATOR ',' ) AS storeProductPicUrl,
                            
                            tdpj.dealer_product_name AS dealerProductName,
                            tdpjtu.name_cn AS dealerUnitName,
                            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpp.product_pic_url SEPARATOR ',' ) AS dealerProductPicUrl,
                            tft.freight_template_name AS dealerFreightTemplateName,
                            
                            tp.product_inner_id,
                            tdp.distr_product_inner_id,
                            tsp.store_product_inner_id,
                            tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
                        FROM
                            
                            tenant_product tp
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_main_pic tpmp ON tp.product_inner_id = tpmp.product_inner_id
                            AND tpmp.product_main_pic_type = 0
                            AND tpmp.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_brand tb ON tp.brand_id = tb.brand_inner_id
                            LEFT JOIN v_back_cate_path vbcp ON tp.back_cate_id = vbcp.leafcateid
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_unit tu ON tp.unit_id = tu.unit_inner_id
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_multi_unit tpmu ON tp.product_inner_id = tpmu.product_inner_id
                            AND tpmu.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_unit tpmutu ON tpmu.unit_inner_id = tpmutu.unit_inner_id
                            
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_product tdp ON tp.product_inner_id = tdp.product_id
                            AND tdp.dealer_id = 1
                            AND tdp.is_complete = 1
                            AND tdp.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_unit tdptu ON tdp.unit_id = tdptu.unit_inner_id
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_product_multi_unit tdpmu on tdp.distr_product_inner_id = tdpmu.distr_product_inner_id
                            AND tdpmu.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_unit tdpmutu ON tdpmu.unit_inner_id = tdpmutu.unit_inner_id
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_product_pic tdpp ON tdp.distr_product_inner_id = tdpp.distr_product_inner_id
                            AND tdpp.distr_product_pic_type = 0
                            AND tdpp.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_product_pic tdppDetail ON tdp.distr_product_inner_id = tdppDetail.distr_product_inner_id
                            AND tdppDetail.distr_product_pic_type = 1
                            AND tdppDetail.is_del = 0
                            
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_store_product tsp ON tp.product_inner_id = tsp.product_id
                            AND tsp.dealer_id = 1
                            AND tsp.is_complete = 1
                            AND tsp.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_store_product_pic tspp ON tsp.store_product_inner_id = tspp.store_product_inner_id
                            AND tspp.store_product_pic_type = 0
                            AND tsp.is_del = 0
                            
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj ON tp.product_inner_id = tdpj.product_id
                            AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1
                            AND tdpj.is_complete = 1
                            AND tdpj.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_onsale_onlinestore tpoo ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tpoo.dealer_product_join_id
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_unit tdpjtu ON tdpj.unit_id = tdpjtu.unit_inner_id
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_pic tpp ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tpp.dealer_product_join_id
                            AND tpp.product_pic_type = 0
                            AND tpp.is_del = 0
                            LEFT JOIN tenant_freight_template tft ON tdpj.fare_template = tft.freight_template_id
                         WHERE tp.is_del = 0 
                        GROUP BY
                            tp.product_inner_id
                    ) product
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON product.product_inner_id = tsp.product_id
                    AND tsp.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product_multi_unit tspmu ON tsp.single_product_inner_id = tspmu.single_product_inner_id
                    AND tspmu.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_single_product tdsp ON product.distr_product_inner_id = tdsp.distr_product_inner_id
                    AND tdsp.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_single_product_multi_unit tdspmu ON tdsp.distr_single_product_inner_id =
                    tdspmu.distr_single_product_inner_id
                    AND tdspmu.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_store_single_product tssp ON product.store_product_inner_id = tssp.store_product_inner_id
                    AND tssp.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON product.dealer_product_join_id = tosp.dealer_product_join_id
                    AND tosp.is_del = 0
                GROUP BY
                    tsp.single_product_inner_id
            ) singleProduct
            
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr_value tpcav ON singleProduct.product_inner_id = tpcav.product_inner_id
            AND tpcav.single_product_inner_id = -1
            AND tpcav.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr tpca ON tpcav.product_custom_attr_id = tpca.product_custom_attr_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr_enum tpcae ON tpcav.product_custom_attr_enum_id =
            tpcae.product_custom_attr_enum_id
            
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_attr_join tsaj ON singleProduct.single_product_inner_id = tsaj.single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN sys_backend_category_attr sbca ON tsaj.attr_id = sbca.cate_attr_inner_id
            AND sbca.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN sys_attr_value sav ON tsaj.attr_value_id = sav.attr_value_id
            
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr_value tpcavsingle ON singleProduct.product_inner_id =
            tpcavsingle.product_inner_id
            AND singleProduct.single_product_inner_id = tpcavsingle.single_product_inner_id
            AND tpcavsingle.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr tpcasingle ON tpcavsingle.product_custom_attr_id =
            tpcasingle.product_custom_attr_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_custom_attr_enum tpcaesingle ON tpcavsingle.product_custom_attr_enum_id =
            tpcaesingle.product_custom_attr_enum_id

SELECT
        t1.stockFlowId,
        t1.mainCover,
        t1.thirdCode,
        t1.productName,
        t1.singleProductThirdCode,
        t1.warehouseName,
        t1.inventoryType,
        t1.inventoryQuantity,
        t1.relatedName,
        t1.InventoryBalance,
        t1.createDate,
        t1.physicalInventoryBalance,
        t1.occupiedInventoryBalance,
        t1.IntransitInventoryBalance,
        t1.warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        t1.relatedId,
        t1.singleProductInnerId
        FROM
        (
        SELECT
        tsf.stock_flow_id AS stockFlowId,
        IFNULL( tp.main_cover, tsp.attr_pic ) AS mainCover,
        tp.third_code AS thirdCode,
        tp.product_name AS productName,
        tsp.single_product_third_code AS singleProductThirdCode,
        tw.warehouse_name AS warehouseName,
        tsf.inventory_type AS inventoryType,
        tsf.inventory_quantity AS inventoryQuantity,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpots.supplier_name
        WHEN 2 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 3 THEN '-'
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 6 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 7 THEN tprots.supplier_name
        WHEN 8 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 9 THEN '-'
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 12 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 13 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 14 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 15 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 16 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 17 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 18 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 19 THEN IFNULL( trotu.user_name, trotu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 20 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 21 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 22 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 23 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 24 THEN outtdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 25 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 26 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedName,
        ( tsf.physical_inventory_balance + tsf.occupied_inventory_balance ) AS InventoryBalance,
        tsf.create_date AS createDate,
        tsf.physical_inventory_balance AS physicalInventoryBalance,
        tsf.occupied_inventory_balance AS occupiedInventoryBalance,
        tsf.Intransit_inventory_balance AS IntransitInventoryBalance,
        IFNULL( twr.warehouse_receipt_outer_id, '-' ) AS warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpo.purchase_order_outer_id
        WHEN 2 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 3 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 6 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 7 THEN tpro.purchase_return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 8 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 9 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 12 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 13 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 14 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 15 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 16 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 17 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 18 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 19 THEN tro.return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 20 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 21 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 22 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 23 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 24 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 25 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 26 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedId,
        tsp.single_product_inner_id AS singleProductInnerId,
        tp.product_inner_id
        FROM
        tenant_stock_flow tsf
        INNER JOIN tenant_product tp ON tsf.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
        AND tp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsf.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
        AND tsp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tsf.warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tsf.oper_user = tea.tea_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt twr ON tsf.warehouse_receipt_id = twr.warehouse_receipt_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order tpo ON tsf.related_id = tpo.purchase_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tpots ON tpo.supplier_id = tpots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order tpro ON tsf.related_id = tpro.purchase_return_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tprots ON tpro.supplier_id = tprots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition tr ON tsf.related_id = tr.requisition_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse outtrtw ON tr.out_warehouse_id = outtrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtrtd ON outtrtw.dealer_id = outtrtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse intrtw ON tr.in_warehouse_id = intrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intrtd ON intrtw.dealer_id = intrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order tcso ON tsf.related_id = tcso.check_stock_order_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tsf.related_id = tor.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tortu ON tor.user_id = tortu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distribution td ON tsf.related_id = td.distribution_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_order tdtdo ON td.distr_order_inner_id = tdtdo.distr_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_initiator_id = intdtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_target_id = outtdtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_return_order tro ON tsf.related_id = tro.return_order_inner_id
        AND tro.return_order_src = 0
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order troto ON tro.order_inner_id = troto.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user trotu ON troto.user_id = trotu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_refund_apply tra ON tsf.related_id = tra.refund_apply_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order trato ON tra.order_inner_id = trato.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tratu ON trato.user_id = tratu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_returned_order tdro ON tsf.related_id = tdro.distr_returned_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdrotd ON tdro.distr_returned_in_dealer = intdrotd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdrotd ON tdro.distr_returned_out_dealer = outtdrotd.dealer_inner_id
         WHERE tsf.is_del = 0
            
            
            
            
            
            
                    AND tsf.inventory_quantity > 0
                    AND tsf.inventory_type NOT IN ( 11, 12, 15, 16, 17, 18, 20, 21, 23 ) 
        GROUP BY
        tsf.stock_flow_id
        ) t1
         WHERE  t1.relatedName = '-' 
        ORDER BY
        t1.createDate DESC,
        t1.product_inner_id DESC LIMIT 0,20

SELECT
            tdpj.dealer_product_code                                    AS onlineProductCode,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id                           AS onlineProductId,
            tsp.single_product_third_code                               AS onlineSingleProductCode,
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id                    AS onlineSingleProductId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_name                                    AS productName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_name )                      AS frontCateName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tb.brand_name )                      AS brandName,
            tosp.retail_price                                           AS retailPrice,
            tosp.min_price_range                                        AS minRetailPrice,
            tosp.max_price_range                                        AS maxRetailPrice,
            CONCAT_WS('；',
                IF ( tdpj.has_express_delivery = 1, '快递发货', NULL ),
                IF ( tdpj.has_in_city_delivery = 1, '同城配送', NULL ),
                IF ( tdpj.has_pick_up = 1, '到店自提', NULL )
            )                                                           AS deliveryMethod,

            tdpj.sale_limit_type                                        AS purchaseLimitType,
            tdpj.sale_limit                                             AS purchaseLimitNum,

            tdpj.is_user_limit                                          AS specifiedUserCondition,
            tdpj.member_limit                                           AS specifiedUserType,
            tdpj.member_limit_level                                     AS specifiedUserLevel,

            tdpj.on_discount                                            AS discountType,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpmdj.member_level )                 AS discountLevel,

            tdpj.selling_point                                          AS salePoint,
            tosp.create_date                                            AS createDate,

            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id                    AS onlineSingleProductInnerId,
            tosaj.onlinestore_single_attr_join_id                       AS attrJoinId,
            sbca.cate_attr_inner_id                                     AS attrId,
            sbca.attr_name                                              AS attrName,
            sav.attr_value_id                                           AS attrValueId,
            sav.attr_value                                              AS attrValue,
            sav.attr_code                                               AS attrCode
        FROM
            tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tosp.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
                AND tosp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsp.single_product_inner_id = tosp.single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id

SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ( SELECT
        t1.stockFlowId,
        t1.mainCover,
        t1.thirdCode,
        t1.productName,
        t1.singleProductThirdCode,
        t1.warehouseName,
        t1.inventoryType,
        t1.inventoryQuantity,
        t1.relatedName,
        t1.InventoryBalance,
        t1.createDate,
        t1.physicalInventoryBalance,
        t1.occupiedInventoryBalance,
        t1.IntransitInventoryBalance,
        t1.warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        t1.relatedId,
        t1.singleProductInnerId
        FROM
        (
        SELECT
        tsf.stock_flow_id AS stockFlowId,
        IFNULL( tp.main_cover, tsp.attr_pic ) AS mainCover,
        tp.third_code AS thirdCode,
        tp.product_name AS productName,
        tsp.single_product_third_code AS singleProductThirdCode,
        tw.warehouse_name AS warehouseName,
        tsf.inventory_type AS inventoryType,
        tsf.inventory_quantity AS inventoryQuantity,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpots.supplier_name
        WHEN 2 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 3 THEN '-'
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 6 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 7 THEN tprots.supplier_name
        WHEN 8 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 9 THEN '-'
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 12 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 13 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 14 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 15 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 16 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 17 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 18 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 19 THEN IFNULL( trotu.user_name, trotu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 20 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 21 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 22 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 23 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 24 THEN outtdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 25 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 26 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedName,
        ( tsf.physical_inventory_balance + tsf.occupied_inventory_balance ) AS InventoryBalance,
        tsf.create_date AS createDate,
        tsf.physical_inventory_balance AS physicalInventoryBalance,
        tsf.occupied_inventory_balance AS occupiedInventoryBalance,
        tsf.Intransit_inventory_balance AS IntransitInventoryBalance,
        IFNULL( twr.warehouse_receipt_outer_id, '-' ) AS warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpo.purchase_order_outer_id
        WHEN 2 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 3 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 6 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 7 THEN tpro.purchase_return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 8 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 9 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 12 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 13 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 14 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 15 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 16 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 17 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 18 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 19 THEN tro.return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 20 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 21 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 22 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 23 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 24 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 25 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 26 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedId,
        tsp.single_product_inner_id AS singleProductInnerId,
        tp.product_inner_id
        FROM
        tenant_stock_flow tsf
        INNER JOIN tenant_product tp ON tsf.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
        AND tp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsf.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
        AND tsp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tsf.warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tsf.oper_user = tea.tea_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt twr ON tsf.warehouse_receipt_id = twr.warehouse_receipt_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order tpo ON tsf.related_id = tpo.purchase_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tpots ON tpo.supplier_id = tpots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order tpro ON tsf.related_id = tpro.purchase_return_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tprots ON tpro.supplier_id = tprots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition tr ON tsf.related_id = tr.requisition_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse outtrtw ON tr.out_warehouse_id = outtrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtrtd ON outtrtw.dealer_id = outtrtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse intrtw ON tr.in_warehouse_id = intrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intrtd ON intrtw.dealer_id = intrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order tcso ON tsf.related_id = tcso.check_stock_order_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tsf.related_id = tor.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tortu ON tor.user_id = tortu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distribution td ON tsf.related_id = td.distribution_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_order tdtdo ON td.distr_order_inner_id = tdtdo.distr_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_initiator_id = intdtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_target_id = outtdtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_return_order tro ON tsf.related_id = tro.return_order_inner_id
        AND tro.return_order_src = 0
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order troto ON tro.order_inner_id = troto.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user trotu ON troto.user_id = trotu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_refund_apply tra ON tsf.related_id = tra.refund_apply_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order trato ON tra.order_inner_id = trato.order_inner_id

SELECT
        t1.stockFlowId,
        t1.mainCover,
        t1.thirdCode,
        t1.productName,
        t1.singleProductThirdCode,
        t1.warehouseName,
        t1.inventoryType,
        t1.inventoryQuantity,
        t1.relatedName,
        t1.InventoryBalance,
        t1.createDate,
        t1.physicalInventoryBalance,
        t1.occupiedInventoryBalance,
        t1.IntransitInventoryBalance,
        t1.warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        t1.relatedId,
        t1.singleProductInnerId
        FROM
        (
        SELECT
        tsf.stock_flow_id AS stockFlowId,
        IFNULL( tp.main_cover, tsp.attr_pic ) AS mainCover,
        tp.third_code AS thirdCode,
        tp.product_name AS productName,
        tsp.single_product_third_code AS singleProductThirdCode,
        tw.warehouse_name AS warehouseName,
        tsf.inventory_type AS inventoryType,
        tsf.inventory_quantity AS inventoryQuantity,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpots.supplier_name
        WHEN 2 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 3 THEN '-'
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 6 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 7 THEN tprots.supplier_name
        WHEN 8 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 9 THEN '-'
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 12 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 13 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 14 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 15 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 16 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ),
        intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 17 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 18 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 19 THEN IFNULL( trotu.user_name, trotu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 20 THEN IF( outtrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( outtrtd.dealer_name, '-', outtrtw.warehouse_name ),
        outtrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 21 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 22 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 23 THEN IFNULL( tratu.user_name, tratu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 24 THEN outtdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 25 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        WHEN 26 THEN intdrotd.dealer_name
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedName,
        ( tsf.physical_inventory_balance + tsf.occupied_inventory_balance ) AS InventoryBalance,
        tsf.create_date AS createDate,
        tsf.physical_inventory_balance AS physicalInventoryBalance,
        tsf.occupied_inventory_balance AS occupiedInventoryBalance,
        tsf.Intransit_inventory_balance AS IntransitInventoryBalance,
        IFNULL( twr.warehouse_receipt_outer_id, '-' ) AS warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        IFNULL( ( CASE tsf.inventory_type
        WHEN 0 THEN '-'
        WHEN 1 THEN tpo.purchase_order_outer_id
        WHEN 2 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 3 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 4 THEN '-'
        WHEN 5 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 6 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 7 THEN tpro.purchase_return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 8 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 9 THEN tcso.check_stock_order_outer_id
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 12 THEN tor.order_outer_id
        WHEN 13 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 14 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 15 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 16 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 17 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 18 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 19 THEN tro.return_order_outer_id
        WHEN 20 THEN tr.requisition_outer_id
        WHEN 21 THEN td.distribution_outer_id
        WHEN 22 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 23 THEN tra.refund_apply_outer_id
        WHEN 24 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 25 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        WHEN 26 THEN tdro.distr_returned_order_outer_id
        ELSE '-' END ), '-') AS relatedId,
        tsp.single_product_inner_id AS singleProductInnerId,
        tp.product_inner_id
        FROM
        tenant_stock_flow tsf
        INNER JOIN tenant_product tp ON tsf.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
        AND tp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsf.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
        AND tsp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tsf.warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tsf.oper_user = tea.tea_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt twr ON tsf.warehouse_receipt_id = twr.warehouse_receipt_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order tpo ON tsf.related_id = tpo.purchase_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tpots ON tpo.supplier_id = tpots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order tpro ON tsf.related_id = tpro.purchase_return_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_supplier tprots ON tpro.supplier_id = tprots.supplier_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition tr ON tsf.related_id = tr.requisition_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse outtrtw ON tr.out_warehouse_id = outtrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtrtd ON outtrtw.dealer_id = outtrtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse intrtw ON tr.in_warehouse_id = intrtw.warehouse_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intrtd ON intrtw.dealer_id = intrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order tcso ON tsf.related_id = tcso.check_stock_order_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tsf.related_id = tor.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tortu ON tor.user_id = tortu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distribution td ON tsf.related_id = td.distribution_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_order tdtdo ON td.distr_order_inner_id = tdtdo.distr_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_initiator_id = intdtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_target_id = outtdtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_return_order tro ON tsf.related_id = tro.return_order_inner_id
        AND tro.return_order_src = 0
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order troto ON tro.order_inner_id = troto.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user trotu ON troto.user_id = trotu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_refund_apply tra ON tsf.related_id = tra.refund_apply_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order trato ON tra.order_inner_id = trato.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user tratu ON trato.user_id = tratu.user_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_distr_returned_order tdro ON tsf.related_id = tdro.distr_returned_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdrotd ON tdro.distr_returned_in_dealer = intdrotd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdrotd ON tdro.distr_returned_out_dealer = outtdrotd.dealer_inner_id
         WHERE tsf.is_del = 0
            
                AND ( tp.product_outer_id LIKE CONCAT( '%', 'TLSPWZYEJ82E9NY9RG27J4Q9', '%' ) OR tp.product_name LIKE CONCAT( '%', 'TLSPWZYEJ82E9NY9RG27J4Q9',
                '%' ) OR tp.third_code LIKE CONCAT( '%', 'TLSPWZYEJ82E9NY9RG27J4Q9', '%' ) OR tsp.single_product_third_code LIKE CONCAT(
                '%', 'TLSPWZYEJ82E9NY9RG27J4Q9', '%' ) ) 
        GROUP BY
        tsf.stock_flow_id
        ) t1
          
        ORDER BY
        t1.createDate DESC,
        t1.product_inner_id DESC LIMIT 0,20

            t1.pick_up_attribute,
            t1.store_outer_id,
            t1.pick_up_name,
            t1.province_code,
            t1.city_code,
            t1.district_code,
            t1.longitude,
            t1.latitude,
            t1.address,
            t1.distance,
            t1.shipperstore_inner_id,
            t1.shipperstore_outer_id,
            t1.shipperstore_name,
            t1.shipperlongitude,
            t1.shipperlatitude,
            t1.shipperstoreAddress,
            t1.shipperdistance,
            t1.shipperwarehouse_is_express,
            t1.shipperwarehouse_is_pick_up,
            t1.shipperwarehouse_is_city_delivery
        FROM
            (
                SELECT
                    tspus.self_pick_up_site_id,
                    tspus.pick_up_attribute,
                    ts.store_outer_id,
                    tspus.pick_up_name,
                    tspus.province_code,
                    tspus.city_code,
                    tspus.district_code,
                    tspus.longitude,
                    tspus.latitude,
                    tspus.address,
                    ROUND( 6371 * 2 * ASIN( SQRT(
                    POW( SIN( ( 0 * PI() / 180 - tspus.latitude * PI() / 180 ) / 2 ), 2 ) -- 纬度
                    + COS( 0 * PI() / 180 ) -- 纬度
                    * COS( tspus.latitude * PI() / 180 ) -- 纬度
                    * POW( SIN( ( 0 * PI() / 180 - tspus.longitude * PI() / 180 ) / 2 ), 2 ) -- 经度
                    ) ) * 1000 -- 米
                    , 2 ) AS distance,
                    shipperts.store_inner_id AS shipperstore_inner_id,
                    shipperts.store_outer_id AS shipperstore_outer_id,
                    shipperts.store_name AS shipperstore_name,
                    shipperts.longitude AS shipperlongitude,
                    shipperts.latitude AS shipperlatitude,
                    shipperts.store_address AS shipperstoreAddress,
                    ROUND( 6371 * 2 * ASIN( SQRT(
                    POW( SIN( ( 0 * PI() / 180 - shipperts.latitude * PI() / 180 ) / 2 ), 2 ) -- 纬度
                    + COS( 0 * PI() / 180 ) -- 纬度
                    * COS( shipperts.latitude * PI() / 180 ) -- 纬度
                    * POW( SIN( ( 0 * PI() / 180 - shipperts.longitude * PI() / 180 ) / 2 ), 2 ) -- 经度
                    ) ) * 1000 -- 米
                    , 2 ) AS shipperdistance,
                    shippertw.warehouse_is_express AS shipperwarehouse_is_express,
                    shippertw.warehouse_is_pick_up AS shipperwarehouse_is_pick_up,
                    shippertw.warehouse_is_city_delivery AS shipperwarehouse_is_city_delivery
                FROM
                    tenant_self_pick_up_site tspus
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tspus.pick_up_warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
                    AND tw.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tw.warehouse_store_id = ts.store_inner_id
                    AND ts.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_self_pick_up_site_join tspusj ON tspus.self_pick_up_site_id = tspusj.self_pick_up_site_id
                    AND tspusj.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse shippertw ON tspusj.shipper_id = shippertw.warehouse_inner_id
                    AND shippertw.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_stock_share tss ON shippertw.warehouse_inner_id = tss.warehouse_id
                    AND tss.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_store shipperts ON tss.store_id = shipperts.store_inner_id
                    AND shipperts.is_del = 0
                     
                 WHERE tspus.is_del = 0
                    AND tspus.pick_up_status = 1 
                GROUP BY
                    tspus.self_pick_up_site_id,
                    shipperts.store_inner_id
            ) t1
        WHERE
            t1.distance IS NOT NULL
            AND t1.shipperdistance IS NOT NULL
        ORDER BY
            t1.distance,
            t1.shipperdistance

SELECT
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id AS onlinestoreSingleProductOuterId,
            IFNULL(tosp.retail_price, 0) AS retailPrice,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_id AS dealerProductJoinId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id AS dealerProductJoinOuterId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_id AS dealerProductJoinId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_name AS productName,
            tdpj.dealer_product_code AS productCode,
            tdpj.main_cover AS productImg,
            IFNULL( CASE 0 WHEN 0 THEN vsps.physical_inventory WHEN 1 THEN vsps.physical_inventory WHEN 2 THEN vsps2.physical_inventory ELSE 0 END, 0 ) AS productStock
        FROM tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp
                 LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tosp.dealer_product_join_id
                 LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    ts.single_product_id,
                    SUM(ts.physical_inventory) AS physical_inventory
                FROM
                    tenant_warehouse tw
                        LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id
                GROUP BY
                    ts.single_product_id
        ) vsps ON tosp.single_product_id = vsps.single_product_id
                 LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT
                vsps.product_id,
                SUM( vsps.physical_inventory ) AS physical_inventory
            FROM
                v_single_product_stock vsps
            WHERE
                vsps.store_channel_type = 0
              AND vsps.store_inner_id = null
              AND ( vsps.warehouse_is_express = 1 OR vsps.warehouse_is_pick_up = 1 OR vsps.warehouse_is_city_delivery = 1 )
            GROUP BY
                product_id
        ) vsps2 ON tdpj.product_id = vsps2.product_id
        WHERE
            tosp.is_del = 0
          AND tdpj.is_del = 0
        GROUP BY
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id

            tdpj.main_cover AS productImg,

        FROM tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp
                 LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tosp.dealer_product_join_id
                 LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    ts.single_product_id,
                    SUM(ts.physical_inventory) AS physical_inventory
                FROM
                    tenant_warehouse tw
                        LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id
                GROUP BY
                    ts.single_product_id
        ) vsps ON tosp.single_product_id = vsps.single_product_id
                 LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT
                vsps.product_id,
                SUM( vsps.physical_inventory ) AS physical_inventory
            FROM
                v_single_product_stock vsps
            WHERE
                vsps.store_channel_type = 0
              AND vsps.store_inner_id = null
              AND ( vsps.warehouse_is_express = 1 OR vsps.warehouse_is_pick_up = 1 OR vsps.warehouse_is_city_delivery = 1 )
            GROUP BY
                product_id
        ) vsps2 ON tdpj.product_id = vsps2.product_id
        WHERE
            tosp.is_del = 0
          AND tdpj.is_del = 0
        GROUP BY
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id

SELECT
            tvr.verification_record_id              AS verification_record_id,
            ifnull(tu.user_nickname,tu.user_name)   AS user_nickname,
            tu.user_phone                           AS user_phone,
            tvr.business_store_type                 AS business_store_type,
            ts.store_name                           AS business_store_name,
            IFNULL( tvsr.verification_sub_organization_type, tvr.verification_organization_type ) AS verification_organization_type,
            IFNULL( ( CASE tvsr.verification_sub_organization_type
            WHEN 0 THEN tdvsub.dealer_name
            WHEN 1 THEN tdvsub.dealer_name
            WHEN 2 THEN tsvsub.store_name
            WHEN 3 THEN tsvsub.store_name
            END ),
            ( CASE tvr.verification_organization_type
            WHEN 0 THEN tdv.dealer_name
            WHEN 1 THEN tdv.dealer_name
            WHEN 2 THEN tsv.store_name
            WHEN 3 THEN tsv.store_name
            END )
            ) AS verification_store_name,
            IFNULL( tvsr.verification_sub_date, tvr.verification_date ) AS verification_date,
            tvr.verification_record_type            AS verification_record_type,
            tvr.verification_record_code AS verification_record_code,
            tvsr.verification_record_sub_code AS verificationRecordSubCode,
            tvr.verification_record_content         AS verification_record_content,
            IFNULL( teasub.tea_name, tea.tea_name )   AS tea_name,
            IFNULL( teasub.tea_phone, tea.tea_phone ) AS tea_phone,
            tu.user_avatar                          AS user_avatar,
            tor.order_outer_id                      AS order_outer_id,
            tor.order_inner_id                      AS order_inner_id,
            topd.order_product_detail_id,
            tor.consignee_name                      AS consignee_name,
            tor.consignee_phone                     AS consignee_phone,
            tor.consignee_selffetching              AS consignee_self_fetching,
            tor.actually_paid                       AS actually_paid,
            tspus.pick_up_name                      AS pick_up_name,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_start              AS marketing_coupon_start,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_end                AS marketing_coupon_end,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name_remark        AS couponNameRemark,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_start_date ELSE topd.valid_start_time END ) AS valid_start_time,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_end_date ELSE topd.valid_end_time END ) AS valid_end_time,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr1.verification_sub_record_id ) AS cancelled,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr2.verification_sub_record_id ) AS unwritten
        FROM
            tenant_verification_record tvr
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tvr.business_store_inner_id = ts.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store tsv ON tvr.verification_organization_id = tsv.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer tdv ON tvr.verification_organization_id = tdv.dealer_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tu.user_inner_id = tvr.user_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tvr.verification_tea_id = tea.tea_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tor.order_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_self_pick_up_site tspus ON tspus.self_pick_up_site_id=tor.self_pick_up_site_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user_coupon tuc ON tuc.user_coupon_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_coupon tmc ON tmc.marketing_coupon_id = tuc.marketing_coupon_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store tsvsub ON tvsr.verification_sub_organization_id = tsvsub.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer tdvsub ON tvsr.verification_sub_organization_id = tdvsub.dealer_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account teasub ON tvsr.verification_sub_tea_id = teasub.tea_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_order_product_detail topd ON tvsr.relation_server_id = topd.order_product_detail_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON topd.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr1 ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr1.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr1.verification_record_sub_state = 1
            AND tvsr1.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr2 ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr2.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr2.verification_record_sub_state = 0
            AND tvsr2.is_del = 0
         WHERE tvr.is_del = 0
            AND ( ( tvsr.verification_record_sub_state IS NULL AND tvr.verification_record_state = 1 )
            OR ( tvsr.verification_record_sub_state IS NOT NULL AND tvsr.verification_record_sub_state = 1 )
            )
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
                and tvr.verification_record_type = 0 
        GROUP BY
            tvr.verification_record_id,
            tvsr.verification_sub_record_id
        ORDER BY
            tvr.verification_date DESC LIMIT 0,20

            tu.create_date                                  AS tucreate_date,
            tust.user_source_name                           AS tustuser_source_name,

            tudj.member_card_number                         AS tudjmember_card_number,
            tudj.member_create_date                         AS tudjmember_create_date,
            tudj.member_level                               AS tudjmember_level,

            tudj.last_consumption_date                      AS tudjlast_consumption_date,
            tudj.total_cost                                 AS tudjtotal_cost,
            tudj.actually_paid                              AS tudjactually_paid,
            tudj.cost_count                                 AS tudjcost_count,
            tudj.customer_price                             AS tudjcustomer_price,
            tudj.total_refund                               AS tudjtotal_refund,
            tudj.refund_count                               AS tudjrefund_count,
            tudj.seller_create_date                         AS tudjseller_create_date,
            tea.tea_name                                    AS other1,
            tea.tea_phone                                   AS tea_phone,
            ts.store_name                                   AS tudjstore_id,

            tudj.store_id                                   AS store_id,
            tust.user_source_id                             AS user_source_id,
            ts.dealer_id                                    AS dealer_id,
            tudj.assistant_id                               AS assistant_id,
            tudj.last_access_time                           AS last_access_time,

            tudj.seller_level AS tudjseller_level,
            IF ( tudj.belong_seller = - 1, NULL, tudj.belong_seller ) AS tudjbelong_seller,
            (SELECT member_level_name FROM tenant_member_card_option WHERE member_level = tudj.member_level) AS memberLevelName
        FROM
            tenant_user_dealer_join tudj
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tu.user_inner_id = tudj.user_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tudj.store_id = ts.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user_source_type tust ON tu.user_source_id = tust.user_source_id
            AND tust.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account tea ON tudj.assistant_id = tea.tea_id
            LEFT JOIN ( SELECT tust.user_inner_id, tust.user_store_track_mode FROM tenant_user_store_track tust GROUP BY tust.user_inner_id ) tusts ON tu.user_inner_id = tusts.user_inner_id
         WHERE tudj.join_id <= 380714

                        AND tu.user_phone LIKE CONCAT( '%', '13372536290', '%' ) 
        GROUP BY
            tudj.join_id
        ORDER BY

        LIMIT 10

SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ( SELECT tp.product_inner_id AS product_inner_id, tp.product_outer_id AS product_outer_id, tp.third_code AS third_code, tdpj.dealer_product_join_id AS dealer_product_join_id, tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id AS dealerProductOutId, tdpj.dealer_product_name AS dealer_product_name, tdpj.main_cover AS main_cover, tdpj.dealer_product_join_type AS dealer_product_join_type, tfc.frontCateNameList AS frontCateNameList, (CASE 0 WHEN 0 THEN SUM(vsps.physical_inventory) WHEN 1 THEN SUM(vsps.physical_inventory) WHEN 2 THEN vsps2.physical_inventory ELSE 0 END) AS stockNum, IFNULL(tspsv.product_sales_volume, 0) AS sellCount FROM tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tosp.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id AND tosp.is_del = 0 LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT ts.single_product_id, SUM(ts.physical_inventory) AS physical_inventory FROM tenant_warehouse tw LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id GROUP BY ts.single_product_id) vsps ON tosp.single_product_id = vsps.single_product_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT dealer_product_join_id, SUM(physical_inventory) AS physical_inventory FROM v_single_product_stock WHERE store_channel_type = 0 AND store_inner_id = null AND (warehouse_is_express = 1 OR warehouse_is_pick_up = 1 OR warehouse_is_city_delivery = 1) GROUP BY dealer_product_join_id) vsps2 ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = vsps2.dealer_product_join_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT tspsv.store_product_id, SUM(tspsv.store_product_sales_volume) AS product_sales_volume FROM tenant_store_product_sales_volume tspsv WHERE tspsv.is_del = 0 AND tspsv.dealer_inner_id = 1 GROUP BY tspsv.store_product_id) tspsv ON tspsv.store_product_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT tfc.cate_name ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id) AS frontCateNameList, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT tfc.cate_outer_id ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id) AS frontCateOutIdList FROM tenant_product_front_cate_join tpfcj LEFT JOIN tenant_frontend_category tfc ON tfc.cate_inner_id = tpfcj.frond_cate_id GROUP BY tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id) tfc ON tfc.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id WHERE tdpj.is_del = 0 AND tp.is_del = 0 AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1 AND tdpj.is_complete = 1 GROUP BY tdpj.dealer_product_join_id ) TOTAL

            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id,
            
            tmggd.tenant_give_discount_detail_id,
            tmggd.full_amount,
            tmggd.order_amount_discount,
            tmggd.reduction_amount,
            ( tmggd.discount_rate * 10 ) AS discount_rate,
            tmggd.is_give_product,
            tmggd.is_give_coupon,
            tmggd.user_max_optional_give_product_num,
            
            ddgpj.discount_detail_product_join_id,
            tp.is_del AS tpIsDel,
            tp.release_status AS tpReleaseStatus,
            tdpj2.dealer_product_join_outer_id AS give_dealer_product_join_outer_id,
            tdpj2.dealer_product_name,
            IFNULL( tosp.attr_pic, tdpj2.main_cover ) AS main_cover,
            tdpj2.is_del AS tdpjIsDel,
            tdpj2.is_complete AS isComplete,
            tpoo.product_onsale_status AS productOnsaleStatus,
            tdpj2.fare_template AS fareTemplate,
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id,
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id,
            ddgpj.give_product_num,
            tosp.is_del AS tospIsDel,
            tdpj2.has_express_delivery AS hasExpressDelivery,
            tdpj2.has_pick_up AS hasPickUp,
            tdpj2.has_in_city_delivery AS hasInCityDelivery,
            
            tmc.marketing_coupon_outer_id,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name,
            (CASE tmggd.is_give_coupon WHEN 1 THEN IFNULL( ( tmc.marketing_coupon_total_amount - IFNULL( surplustuc.count, 0 ) ), 0 ) ELSE null END)as surplusNumber,
            gddcj.give_coupon_num,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_type,
            
            sav.attr_id,
            sav.attr_value_id,
            sav.attr_value,
            sbca.attr_name
        FROM
            tenant_marketing_give_full tmgf
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_give_discount_detail tmggd ON tmggd.marketing_give_id = tmgf.marketing_give_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_marketing_activity_join pmcj ON pmcj.marketing_activity_id = tmgf.marketing_activity_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = pmcj.dealer_product_join_id
            
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_give_discount_detail_product_join ddgpj ON ddgpj.marketing_give_id = tmgf.marketing_give_inner_id
            AND ddgpj.discount_detail_id = tmggd.tenant_give_discount_detail_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id = ddgpj.onlinestore_single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj2 ON tdpj2.dealer_product_join_id = ddgpj.dealer_product_join_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_onsale_onlinestore tpoo ON tdpj2.dealer_product_join_id = tpoo.dealer_product_join_id
            AND tpoo.store_id = 54
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tosp.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
            
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_attr_join tosaj ON tosaj.onlinestore_single_product_id = tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN sys_backend_category_attr sbca ON sbca.cate_attr_inner_id = tosaj.attr_id
            LEFT JOIN sys_attr_value sav ON tosaj.attr_value_id = sav.attr_value_id
            AND tosaj.attr_id = sav.attr_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_give_discount_detail_coupon_join gddcj ON gddcj.marketing_give_id = tmgf.marketing_give_inner_id
            AND gddcj.discount_detail_id = tmggd.tenant_give_discount_detail_id
            AND gddcj.is_del =0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_coupon tmc ON tmc.marketing_coupon_id = gddcj.marketing_coupon_id

SELECT
            tvr.verification_record_id                                              AS verification_record_id,
            ifnull(tu.user_nickname, tu.user_name)                                  AS user_nickname,
            tu.user_phone                                                           AS user_phone,
            tu.user_avatar                                                          AS user_avatar,
            tvr.business_store_type                                                 AS business_store_type,
            tvr.verification_record_business_id                                     AS verificationRecordBusinessId,
            ts.store_name                                                           AS businessStoreName,
            tvr.business_date                                                       AS business_date,
            tvr.verification_record_type                                            AS verification_record_type,
            tvr.verification_record_code                                            AS verification_record_code,
            tvr.verification_record_content                                         AS verification_record_content,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_start                                              AS marketing_coupon_start,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_end                                                AS marketing_coupon_end,
            (CASE  WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_end < now() THEN 2 WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_start > now() THEN 6 ELSE tuc.marketing_coupon_status END) AS marketingCouponStatus,
            tvr.verification_record_state                                           AS verification_record_state,
            tor.order_outer_id                                                      AS order_outer_id,
            tor.order_inner_id                                                      AS order_inner_id,
            tor.consignee_name                                                      AS consignee_name,
            tor.consignee_phone                                                     AS consignee_phone,
            tor.consignee_selffetching                                              AS consignee_self_fetching,
            tor.actually_paid                                                       AS actually_paid,
            tspus.pick_up_name                                                      AS pick_up_name,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_start_date ELSE topd.valid_start_time END ) AS valid_start_time,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_end_date ELSE topd.valid_end_time END ) AS valid_end_time,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr1.verification_sub_record_id ) AS cancelled,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr2.verification_sub_record_id ) AS unwritten
        FROM
            tenant_verification_record tvr
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tvr.business_store_inner_id = ts.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tu.user_inner_id = tvr.user_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN  tenant_user_coupon tuc ON tuc.user_coupon_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            AND tuc.marketing_coupon_status IN (0, 2)

SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ( SELECT
            tmc.marketing_coupon_id AS couponTempNo,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_outer_id AS marketingCouponOuterId,
            tmc.marketing_activity_id AS marketingActivityId,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name AS marketingCouponName,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name_remark AS marketingCouponNameRemark,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_type AS marketingCouponType,
            ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_type
                WHEN 0 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( '减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 1 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 2 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( '随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 3 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN '可兑换'
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,可兑换' )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,可兑换' )
                    END
                )
            END
            )                           AS discountsContent,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_status AS marketingCouponStatus,
            IFNULL( ( tmc.marketing_coupon_total_amount - IFNULL( surplustuc.count, 0 ) ), 0 ) AS surplusNumber,
            IFNULL( alreadyUsetuc.count, 0 ) AS alreadyUseNumber,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS marketingCouponDeductionAmount,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_discount AS marketingCouponDiscount,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS marketingCouponRandomStart,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS marketingCouponRandomEnd,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_start AS marketingCouponStart,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_end AS marketingCouponEnd,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_type AS marketingCouponExpiryType,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_start_day AS marketingCouponExpiryStartDay,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_day AS marketingCouponExpiryDay,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_icon_before AS marketingCouponIconBefore,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_icon_after AS marketingCouponIconAfter,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_get_user_limit AS marketingCouponGetUserLimit,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_get_limit AS marketingCouponGetLimit,
            tma.dealer_id AS dealerId,
            tma.store_id AS storeId
        FROM
            tenant_marketing_coupon tmc
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_activity tma ON tmc.marketing_activity_id = tma.marketing_activity_id
            AND tma.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id,
                    COUNT( tuc.user_coupon_inner_id ) count
                FROM
                    tenant_user_coupon tuc
                WHERE
                    tuc.is_del = 0
                    AND tuc.user_inner_id IS NOT NULL
                GROUP BY
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id
            ) surplustuc ON tmc.marketing_coupon_id = surplustuc.marketing_coupon_id
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id,
                    COUNT( tuc.user_coupon_inner_id ) count
                FROM
                    tenant_user_coupon tuc
                WHERE
                    tuc.is_del = 0
                    AND tuc.user_inner_id IS NOT NULL
                    AND tuc.marketing_coupon_status = 1
                GROUP BY
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id
            ) alreadyUsetuc ON tmc.marketing_coupon_id = alreadyUsetuc.marketing_coupon_id
